data.title: About: WKJY
data.meta_description: WKJY (98.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to Hempstead, New York, and serving Nassau County, New York. It broadcasts an adult contemporary music format and is owned by Connoisseur Media. WKJY's studios and offices are located at Airport Plaza in Farmingdale, New York, and its transmitter is located near the Southern State Parkway in Hempstead.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

WKJY (98.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to Hempstead, New York, and serving Nassau County, New York. It broadcasts an adult contemporary music format and is owned by Connoisseur Media. WKJY's studios and offices are located at Airport Plaza in Farmingdale, New York, and its transmitter is located near the Southern State Parkway in Hempstead. (en)

WKJY（98.3 FM，“KJOY 98.3”）是位于美国纽约州纳苏县亨普斯特德的一个成人当代音乐广播电台，工作室位于纽约州纳苏县，由Connoisseur Media, LLC开办。范围覆盖长岛及纽约东部，发射功率3千瓦。 (zh)
